Package com.rb.nonbiz.search

Class BinarySearchResult<X,​Y>

java.lang.Object
com.rb.nonbiz.search.BinarySearchResult<X,​Y>
public class BinarySearchResult<X,​Y>
extends java.lang.Object
The result of a binary search.

As we narrow in on x to find the best f(x), the result will be an interval [x1, x2] and a corresponding interval [f(x1), f(x2)] such that f(x1) ≤ f(x) ≤ f(x2), where f(x) is the 'targetY' parameter in the BinarySearchParameters.
